    q: 'How do I keep AGENTS.md from going stale?',
    a: 'Treat it like code: review changes in pull requests, update it when an agent makes the same mistake twice, and link from it to decision records so the why lives in version control. When a section stops being useful, delete it. The file should always reflect the current operating contract, not the original author\'s good intentions.'
